snippet.title: Dead Event Trailer
snippet.description:
New Indie Game On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1333490/Dead_Event/
Dead Event is a MMORPG open world survival game in which the player grows up as a creature. The creature will grow bigger overtime and with interactions in-game also lose some growth on death. Form a colony or hunt alone, become part of a player-created ecosystem. Survive, eat or be eaten...
Discord: https://discord.gg/bnY8PBAqYF











"Music by: www.bensound.com"
